data.description: Built in 2019. updated to a four-bedroom home recently. This spacious home has a den/office on the main level. Stainless steel appliances, with laminate wood flooring throughout and custom cabinets. Enjoy quiet evenings and afternoons in the privacy of your own fenced in backyard. All bedrooms include great closet space. Home has plenty of storage space and a kitchen pantry. Seller is motivated and ready to sell. So come see your new home today. Just minutes from the highway, markets and restaurants. Located in Mt. Vernon schools. Roof, water heater and furnace are only four years old.
